Arash Motor Company Logo
Arash Motor Company is a Supercar & Hypercar manufacturer based in Newmarket, Suffolk, England. It was originally established by Arash Farboud as Farboud Limited in 1999 and changed name in 2006. The company has made four models to date - the AF-LM, the Farboud GTS, the AF-8 and the AF-10. Currently only the AF-8 & AF-10 are in production but a new car is due to be released in 2021.
